OL,3,CScooter battery plugged in overnight
OL,4,Ccauses #40,000 damage to man's home
OL,6,FWatch: John Leavett shows ITV News
OL,7,FMeridian's Richard Slee the extent of
OL,8,Fthe damage
OL,10,FA man says he's 'lucky to be alive'
OL,11,Fbut has been left with #40,000 worth
OL,12,Fof damage following a fire caused by a
OL,13,Fmobility scooter battery.
OL,15,FJohn Leavett forgot to unplug the
OL,16,Fbattery when he went to bed but woke
OL,17,Fin the middle of night to find his
OL,18,Fhome alight.
