OL,6,FFirefighters have released footage of
OL,7,Fthe immediate aftermath of the fire
OL,8,Fwhich shows an outbuilding connected
OL,9,Fto the bungalow still smouldering.
OL,11,FFlames spread to the roof of the
OL,12,Fproperty in Hamble, Hampshire but
OL,13,Fthankfully they manage to save most of
OL,14,Fit.
OL,16,FJohn describes a frightening scene,
OL,17,F"It was cascading out like rocket
OL,18,Fshells going up, and it's all really
OL,19,Floud noises.
