OL,6,FLithium-ion rechargeable batteries are
OL,7,Fincreasingly common and found in
OL,8,Felectric bikes, scooters, cars,
OL,9,Flaptops, tablets, mobile phones and
OL,10,Fother common household devices.
OL,12,FHampshire Fire and Rescue Service says
OL,13,Fit's seen a rise in fire caused by
OL,14,Frechargeable batteries and is making a
OL,15,Fplea to people this Christmas to only
OL,16,Fbuy batteries from reputable
OL,17,Fretailers, and to use them responsibly.
