OL,6,FFrom April 2024 to March 2025, the
OL,7,Fforce says it dealt with 156 battery
OL,8,Frelated blazes in the area, an
OL,9,Fincrease of 64 from the previous 12-
OL,10,Fmonth period, and an increase of 80
OL,11,Fthe year prior to that.
OL,13,FLast month alone, firefighters dealt
OL,14,Fwith three battery fires across
OL,15,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight
OL,16,Fincluding one involving an e-scooter
OL,17,Fand another involving a camera battery.
OL,19,FThe fire service has released this
OL,20,Ffootage of another lithium-ion battery
OL,21,Ffire, involving an e-scooter
