OL,6,F"When buying electrical products such
OL,7,Fas phones, tablets, e-scooters and
OL,8,Fother lithium-ion battery devices, we
OL,9,Fask that you only do so from reputable
OL,10,Fretailers, ensuring they meet UK
OL,11,FSafety Standards.
OL,13,F"Use the charger your product came
OL,14,Fwith, don't overload sockets and never
OL,15,Fleave them plugged in overnight or
OL,16,Funattended."
